<typeStatus box="[629,677,405,429]" pageId="31" pageNumber="182">type</typeStatus>
locality, off Sumatra, and the Mediterranean Sea, near 
<collectingCountry box="[1332,1398,404,429]" name="Tunisia" pageId="31" pageNumber="182">Tunis</collectingCountry>
, as detailed above.
</paragraph>
